videos.description: Christian Koloko soars through the paint and throws down the alley-oop for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Bennedict Mathurin lobs a beauty to Christian Koloko for an Arizona alley-oop

videos.description: Bennedict Mathurin gathers the rock and buries the 3-pointer to put the Wildcats on the board first.
videos.headline: Bennedict Mathurin pulls up and knocks down the 3 for Arizona

videos.description: Quincy Guerrier somehow knocks down the and-1 despite losing his footing to pull the Ducks within one.
videos.headline: Quincy Guerrier somehow drains the and-1 for Oregon

videos.description: Azuolas Tubelis hauls in the nearly full-court pass and throws it down with authority to regain the lead.
videos.headline: Dalen Terry with an absolute dime to Azuolas Tubelis for an Arizona slam

videos.description: Dalen Terry hauls in the lob and throws down the hammer for the Wildcats.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dalen Terry gets up for alley-oop jam vs. Oregon Ducks) 2022/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dalen Terry jumps out of the gym for this Arizona alley-oop

videos.description: Eric Williams Jr. steals the rock and unleashes a massive jam to extend the Ducks' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Eric Williams Jr. makes a great defensive play for the steal) 2022/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Eric Williams gets it done and both sides of the ball for Oregon

videos.description: N'Faly Dante's second effort pays off as he knocks down the and-1 to extend the Ducks' lead early in the second half.

videos.headline: N'Faly Dante won't be denied as he drains the and-1 for Oregon

videos.description: Quincy Guerrier is smooth as silk as he drains the fadeaway 3-pointer for the Ducks.

videos.headline: Quincy Guerrier steps back and drills the fadeaway 3 for Oregon

videos.description: Christian Koloko hauls in the lob and rocks the rim to regain the lead.

videos.headline: Christian Koloko elevates and slams home the alley-oop for Arizona

videos.description: Christian Koloko and the Wildcats defense deny Oregon a shot on the final possession to seal the victory in a nail-biter at home.
videos.headline: Christian Koloko locks down Oregon to seal the victory at home
